column2: 1895 Bancorp of Wisconsin, Inc. is a holding company, which engages in the provision of banking and financial services through its subsidiary PyraMax Bank. The company is headquartered in Greenfield, Wisconsin. The Company, through PyraMax Bank, is engaged in providing a range of financial services, including the granting of commercial, residential and consumer loans, and acceptance of deposits from individual customers and small businesses. The company also offers a selection of deposit accounts, including non-interest-bearing checking accounts, interest-bearing checking accounts, money market accounts, statement savings, health savings and certificates of deposit.
